    "description": "A 2D action adventure platformer with a simple sword combat and permadeath, it offers,<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- One big level to explore.<br />\r\n- Collectibles to be found that contain's lore.<br />\r\n- Many Enemies to fight.<br />\r\n- Magic power up.<br />\r\n- Secrets.<br />\r\n- Hidden Puzzle to solve.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStory<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn a world full of wonders, a new Star is shining, a young soul full of hope, dreams and adventure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Royal Sorcerer Isvada kidnapped the rightful heir after the King's mysterious death and caused the Kingdom to fall into Chaos.<br />\r\nYou became the Wanderer set to achieve your dreams and save your homeland from the evil wizard by being brave and going into your first Adventure.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMore <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis is part 1 out of 3 short games as follows,<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1- New Star.<br />\r\n2- Evil Shadows.<br />\r\n3- Stars Collide.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nContain Achievements.<br />\r\nFully Playable using controller.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nControls<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWalk -<br />\r\n            Keyboard / Arrow Keys<br />\r\n            Controller / D-Pad<br />\r\nJump -<br />\r\n            Keyboard / Spacebar<br />\r\n            Controller / X on DualShock 4<br />\r\nAttack -<br />\r\n            Keyboard / A Key<br />\r\n            Controller / Square on DualShock 4<br />\r\nMagic -<br />\r\n            Keyboard / D Key<br />\r\n            Controller / Circle on DualShock 4<br />\r\nInteract -<br />\r\n            Keyboard / W Key<br />\r\n            Controller / Triangle  on DualShock 4<br />\r\nReset after Death -<br />\r\n            Keyboard / S Key<br />\r\n            Controller / R1 on Dualshock 4<br />\r\nPause - <br />\r\n            Keyboard / Enter Key<br />\r\n            Controller / Options on DualShock 4<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote! DualShock4 was used as a sample for a generic controller so the same applies for Xbox controller or any controller with the same layout.<br />\r\nTo use connect the controller via bluetooth and it should work.",
